      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start on the atmosphere, but i need more specific details to really set the scene for the characters. i want to ground the danger in reality. can you describe some of the people walking through these streets or hanging out on the corners? give me some descriptions of what they look like, how they're dressed, and what kind of vibe they give off to someone just passing through. make it feel authentic to a high-crime area.",
